# This root .dockerignore applies ONLY to builds whose context is the repo root.
# Currently that's the mockprovider image (its Dockerfile COPYs mockprovider/ and
# fixtures/). The core (./core) and fanout (./fanout) builds use their own context
# and their own .dockerignore, so this file does not affect them.
#
# Exclude everything, then re-include only what the mock build needs. This keeps
# the build context tiny (no core/vendor, no .git, no node_modules).
*
!mockprovider
!fixtures
